    },
    {
      "id": "t25",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "The primary income source for many creators is advertising revenue through the"
    },
    {
      "id": "t26",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "YouTube Partner Program"
    },
    {
      "id": "t27",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Creators receive a portion of advertising revenue shown before or during videos."
    },
    {
      "id": "t28",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Average CPM: $1 – $5"
    },
    {
      "id": "t29",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Finance niche CPM: $10 – $30"
    },
    {
      "id": "t30",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Business niche CPM: $8 – $20"
    },
    {
      "id": "t31",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "2. Sponsorships"
    },
    {
      "id": "t32",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Brands often pay creators to promote products or services in their videos."
    },
    {
      "id": "t33",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Small channels: $500 – $2,000 per sponsored video"
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Mid-size channels: $2,000 – $20,000"
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Large channels: $20,000 – $100,000+"
    },
    {
      "id": "t36",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "3. Affiliate Marketing"
    },
    {
      "id": "t37",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Creators promote products using affiliate links and earn commissions when viewers make purchases."
    },
    {
      "id": "t38",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Affiliate commissions typically range from"
    },
    {
      "id": "t39",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "5% to 30%"
    },
    {
      "id": "t40",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "depending on the program."
    },
    {
      "id": "t41",
      "tag": "h3",
      "text": "4. Digital Products and Courses"
    },
    {
      "id": "t42",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Many YouTubers sell their own products such as courses, templates, or merchandise."
    },
    {
      "id": "t43",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "This income source can become the largest revenue stream once a creator builds a loyal audience."
    },
